Pre-Game Insights: The encounter is a crucial one for the Indomitable Lions who can secure a spot for the 2025 Africa Cup of Nations in case of victory.
Cameroon needs to get at least four points to be sure of a qualification ticket.
Miscellaneous Highlights: The two countries are leading the group with Kenya having an upper hand for scoring two goals as compared to Cameroon that scored just one.
However, they are tied on four points and a plus one goal difference.
Others: The coach Marc Brys had published a list of 24 players to defend the colours of Cameroon in the competition.
All the players called to camp trained intensively at the Ngoa-Ekelle Stadium in Yaounde.
